class=3D"khtml-block-placeholder"></FONT></DIV><DIV><FONT =
class=3D"Apple-style-span" face=3D"Courier">CONFERENCE =
EVENTS</FONT></DIV><DIV><FONT class=3D"Apple-style-span" =
face=3D"Courier">-----------------</FONT></DIV><DIV><FONT =
class=3D"Apple-style-span" face=3D"Courier"><BR =
class=3D"khtml-block-placeholder"></FONT></DIV><DIV><FONT =
class=3D"Apple-style-span" face=3D"Courier">CONTEXT'07 will include =
paper presentation sessions, a poster and</FONT></DIV><DIV><FONT =
class=3D"Apple-style-span" face=3D"Courier">demonstration session, two =
days of workshops, and a doctoral</FONT></DIV><DIV><FONT =
class=3D"Apple-style-span" face=3D"Courier">consortium. Workshops and =
the doctoral consortium will circulate separate</FONT></DIV><DIV><FONT =
class=3D"Apple-style-span" face=3D"Courier">calls for papers and =
participation, which will also be available at =
the</FONT></DIV><DIV><FONT class=3D"Apple-style-span" =
face=3D"Courier">conference web site.</FONT></DIV><DIV><FONT =
class=3D"Apple-style-span" face=3D"Courier"><BR =
class=3D"khtml-block-placeholder"></FONT></DIV><DIV><FONT =
class=3D"Apple-style-span" face=3D"Courier"><BR =
class=3D"khtml-block-placeholder"></FONT></DIV><DIV><FONT =
class=3D"Apple-style-span" face=3D"Courier">ACCEPTANCE CRITERIA AND =
SUBMISSION CATEGORIES</FONT></DIV><DIV><FONT class=3D"Apple-style-span" =
face=3D"Courier">---------------------------------------------</FONT></DIV=
><DIV><FONT class=3D"Apple-style-span" face=3D"Courier"><BR =
class=3D"khtml-block-placeholder"></FONT></DIV><DIV><FONT =
class=3D"Apple-style-span" face=3D"Courier">Because CONTEXT'07 will be =
an interdisciplinary forum, all submissions will</FONT></DIV><DIV><FONT =
class=3D"Apple-style-span" face=3D"Courier">be evaluated both for their =
technical merit and for their accessibility to</FONT></DIV><DIV><FONT =
class=3D"Apple-style-span" face=3D"Courier">an interdisciplinary =
audience. Works that transcend disciplinary =
boundaries</FONT></DIV><DIV><FONT class=3D"Apple-style-span" =
face=3D"Courier">are especially encouraged.</FONT></DIV><DIV><FONT =
class=3D"Apple-style-span" face=3D"Courier"><BR =
class=3D"khtml-block-placeholder"></FONT></DIV><DIV><FONT =
class=3D"Apple-style-span" face=3D"Courier">Submissions may be for full =
papers, poster abstracts, or demonstration</FONT></DIV><DIV><FONT =
class=3D"Apple-style-span" face=3D"Courier">abstracts. Full papers will =
be accepted either for oral presentation or for</FONT></DIV><DIV><FONT =
class=3D"Apple-style-span" face=3D"Courier">presentation at a poster =
session. All accepted full paper submissions will</FONT></DIV><DIV><FONT =
class=3D"Apple-style-span" face=3D"Courier">be published in the =
proceedings. Accepted posters and demonstrations will =
be</FONT></DIV><DIV><FONT class=3D"Apple-style-span" =
face=3D"Courier">presented at the poster session, and the associated =
abstracts will be</FONT></DIV><DIV><FONT class=3D"Apple-style-span" =
face=3D"Courier">published in a brochure distributed to attendees. For =
additional details</FONT></DIV><DIV><FONT class=3D"Apple-style-span" =
face=3D"Courier">see the conference web site.</FONT></DIV><DIV><FONT =
class=3D"Apple-style-span" face=3D"Courier"><BR =
class=3D"khtml-block-placeholder"></FONT></DIV><DIV><FONT =
class=3D"Apple-style-span" face=3D"Courier">For a paper to appear in the =
proceedings, at least one author must register</FONT></DIV><DIV><FONT =
class=3D"Apple-style-span" face=3D"Courier">for the conference by the =
deadline for camera-ready copy.</FONT></DIV><DIV><FONT =
class=3D"Apple-style-span" face=3D"Courier"><BR =
class=3D"khtml-block-placeholder"></FONT></DIV><DIV><FONT =
class=3D"Apple-style-span" face=3D"Courier"><BR =
class=3D"khtml-block-placeholder"></FONT></DIV><DIV><FONT =
class=3D"Apple-style-span" face=3D"Courier">SUBMISSION =
PROCEDURES</FONT></DIV><DIV><FONT class=3D"Apple-style-span" =
face=3D"Courier">---------------------</FONT></DIV><DIV><FONT =
class=3D"Apple-style-span" face=3D"Courier"><BR =
class=3D"khtml-block-placeholder"></FONT></DIV><DIV><FONT =
class=3D"Apple-style-span" face=3D"Courier">Papers must be submitted =
electronically as PDF files. Submissions cannot</FONT></DIV><DIV><FONT =
class=3D"Apple-style-span" face=3D"Courier">exceed 14 pages in the =
Springer LNAI format. Detailed formatting and</FONT></DIV><DIV><FONT =
class=3D"Apple-style-span" face=3D"Courier">submissions instructions, as =
well as LaTeX and Word templates, will be</FONT></DIV><DIV><FONT =
class=3D"Apple-style-span" face=3D"Courier">available in the author =
instructions section of the conference Web</FONT></DIV><DIV><FONT =
class=3D"Apple-style-span" face=3D"Courier">site.</FONT></DIV><DIV><FONT =
class=3D"Apple-style-span" face=3D"Courier"><BR =
class=3D"khtml-block-placeholder"></FONT></DIV><DIV><FONT =
class=3D"Apple-style-span" face=3D"Courier">All accepted authors will =
have the option of presenting a system</FONT></DIV><DIV><FONT =
class=3D"Apple-style-span" face=3D"Courier">demonstration at the poster =
session. Authors wishing to present a</FONT></DIV><DIV><FONT =
class=3D"Apple-style-span" face=3D"Courier">demonstration without an =
accompanying paper must submit a demonstration</FONT></DIV><DIV><FONT =
class=3D"Apple-style-span" face=3D"Courier">abstract. Demonstration =
abstracts should describe cutting-edge systems =
not</FONT></DIV><DIV><FONT class=3D"Apple-style-span" =
face=3D"Courier">described in paper submissions. Demonstration abstracts =
should summarize</FONT></DIV><DIV><FONT class=3D"Apple-style-span" =
face=3D"Courier">the system's behavior and significance, and should =
include at least one</FONT></DIV><DIV><FONT class=3D"Apple-style-span" =
face=3D"Courier">screen shot. If desired, they may also include the URL =
of an informal video</FONT></DIV><DIV><FONT class=3D"Apple-style-span" =
face=3D"Courier">on the web. Demonstration abstracts should be at most 2 =
pages long.</FONT></DIV><DIV><FONT class=3D"Apple-style-span" =
face=3D"Courier"><BR =
class=3D"khtml-block-placeholder"></FONT></DIV><DIV><FONT =
class=3D"Apple-style-span" face=3D"Courier"><BR =
class=3D"khtml-block-placeholder"></FONT></DIV><DIV><FONT =
class=3D"Apple-style-span" face=3D"Courier">MULTIPLE SUBMISSIONS =
POLICY</FONT></DIV><DIV><FONT class=3D"Apple-style-span" =
face=3D"Courier">---------------------------</FONT></DIV><DIV><FONT =
class=3D"Apple-style-span" face=3D"Courier"><BR =
class=3D"khtml-block-placeholder"></FONT></DIV><DIV><FONT =
class=3D"Apple-style-span" face=3D"Courier">CONTEXT'07 will not accept =
any paper which, at the time of submission, is</FONT></DIV><DIV><FONT =
class=3D"Apple-style-span" face=3D"Courier">under review for or has =
already been published or accepted for =
publication</FONT></DIV><DIV><FONT class=3D"Apple-style-span" =
face=3D"Courier">in a journal or another conference. This restriction =
does not apply to</FONT></DIV><DIV><FONT class=3D"Apple-style-span" =
face=3D"Courier">submissions for workshops and other venues with a =
limited audience.</FONT></DIV><DIV><FONT class=3D"Apple-style-span" =
face=3D"Courier"><BR =
class=3D"khtml-block-placeholder"></FONT></DIV><DIV><FONT =
